'''Conky'''是一种自由软件，用于[[X视窗系统|X视窗系统]]的{{link-en|系統監視器|System monitor}}，可以在[[FreeBSD|FreeBSD]]、[[OpenBSD|OpenBSD]]和各种[[Linux|Linux]]发布上使用的自由软件。Conky具有很高的可配置性<ref name="Popov">[http://www.linux.com/feature/136147 Expert's guide to configuring Conky] {{Wayback|url=http://www.linux.com/feature/136147 |date=20090203213230 }} by Dmitri Popov on [[Linux.com|Linux.com]]</ref><ref name="Stamper">[http://debaday.debian.net/2007/09/02/conky-highly-configurable-system-monitor-for-x/ Conky: highly configurable system monitor for X] {{Wayback|url=http://debaday.debian.net/2007/09/02/conky-highly-configurable-system-monitor-for-x/ |date=20080913140652 }} by Casey Stamper on Debian.net</ref><ref name="Wieseler">[http://blog.kickino.org/archives/2006/09/25/T23_09_45/ GKrellM vs. Conky] {{Wayback|url=http://blog.kickino.org/archives/2006/09/25/T23_09_45/ |date=20081202050734 }} by Sebastian Wieseler</ref>，可以监视许多系统参数，如：[[CPU|CPU]]、[[内存|内存]]、[[分頁|分頁]]、[[碟盤存儲|硬盘使用情况]]等状态；各种硬件的温度；系统的进程（[[top_(Unix)|top]]）；[[网卡|网络状态]]；电池电量；系统信息和邮件收发；各种音乐播放器[[Music_Player_Daemon|MPD]]、[[XMMS2|XMMS2]]、[[BMPx|BMPx]]、[[Audacious_Media_Player|Audacious]]）的控制<ref name="docs">{{Cite web |url=http://conky.sourceforge.net/docs.html |title=Conky documentation |accessdate=2008-09-15 |archive-date=2006-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060125020209/http://conky.sourceforge.net/docs.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不像其他系统监视器那样需要高级别的[[部件工具箱|部件工具箱]]（widget toolkits）来渲染他们的信息，Conky可以直接在X视窗下渲染，这意味着在相同配置下Conky可以消耗更少的资源<ref name="mulander">[https://web.archive.org/web/20090723025730/http://my.opera.com/mulander/blog/show.dml/403237 conky] review by mulander</ref><ref name="Sharma">[http://www.linux.com/articles/56931 CLI Magic: Lightweight Conky is a system monitor powerhouse] {{Wayback|url=http://www.linux.com/articles/56931 |date=20081107104836 }} by Shashank Sharma on [[Linux.com|Linux.com]]</ref>。

用户可以自行创建和分发 Conky的自定义脚本，通常以[[.conkyrc|.conkyrc]]命名，放在用户目录下，用户通过改变功能模块和界面来配置不同的Conky显示界面<ref name="rc_screens">{{Cite web |url=http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?p=1645914 |title=Post your .conkyrc files w/ screenshots |accessdate=2008-09-15 |archive-date=2009-02-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090215115819/http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?p=1645914 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="scripts">{{Cite web |url=http://gnome-look.org/content/show.php/Conky+scripts?content=52896 |title=Conky scripts |accessdate=2008-09-15 |archive-date=2008-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080521034837/http://www.gnome-look.org/content/show.php/Conky+scripts?content=52896 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="gmail">{{Cite web |url=http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?p=4219577 |title=Conky Gmail Revisited |accessdate=2008-09-15 |archive-date=2010-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211002743/http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?p=4219577 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="howto">{{Cite web |url=http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?p=1194508 |title=Howto: Get a beautiful Conky 1.4.2 setup |accessdate=2008-09-15 |archive-date=2011-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522035232/http://ubuntuforums.org/showthread.php?p=1194508 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

